map_mission0.Dialogue: The desk has a filing cabinet. Maybe there is useful information there.
map_mission0.Name: Open files
map_mission0.Description: I pull open the filing cabinet. There are two separate tabs.

map_tab1.Name: STUFF
map_tab1.Description: The tab is full of loose papers.

map_paper1.Name: Папірчик
map_paper1.Description: Basic financing. Puff must have been designated as the accountant of the gang. Безкорисно.

map_paper2.Name: Папірчик
map_paper2.Description: A letter outlining Puff's frustration in the gang. Безкорисно.

map_paper4.Name: Папірчик
map_paper4.Description: Labeled "IMPORTANT PEOPLE." There are addresses scribbled across the top:##5314 21st and 4th #101 6th Street Under ##These must be the addresses of Zombie Kingz houses. Useful.

map_tab2.Name: MORE STUFF
map_tab2.Description: You pull open the drawer, and inside is a pamphlet and an embossed coin.
